Package com.bws.jdistil.core.datasource.database

Class BoundDatabaseDataManager<I,T extends DataObject<I>>

java.lang.Object
com.bws.jdistil.core.datasource.database.DatabaseDataManager<I,T>
com.bws.jdistil.core.datasource.database.BoundDatabaseDataManager<I,T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataManager<I,T>
public abstract class BoundDatabaseDataManager<I,T extends DataObject<I>> extends DatabaseDataManager<I,T>
Abstract bound database data manager class that uses binding information to implement data manager functionality.
Author:
Bryan Snipes

    • getValueCondition

      private ValueCondition getValueCondition(DataObjectBinding dataObjectBinding, ValueCriterion valueCriterion)
      Returns a value condition using a data object binding and value criterion. Initially processes the column and associate bindings of the given data object binding before recursively checking the data object binding of each dependent binding. Processing continues until a value condition is created.
      Parameters:
      dataObjectBinding - Data object binding.
      valueCriterion - Value criterion.
      Returns:
